data.title: George J. Lewis
data.meta_description: George J. Lewis. Actor: Der Rächer mit der Maske. George J. Lewis was born on 10 December 1903 in Guadalajara, Jalisco, Mexico. He was an actor, known for Der Rächer mit der Maske (1944), Radar Patrol vs. Spy King (1949) and Arglist im Palast (1949). He was married to Mary Louise Lohman. He died on 8 December 1995 in Rancho Santa Fe, California, USA.
data.text: George J. Lewis was born on December 10, 1903 in Guadalajara, Jalisco, Mexico. He was an actor, known for Der Rächer mit der Maske (1944), Radar Patrol vs. Spy King (1949) and Arglist im Palast (1949). He was married to Mary Louise Lohman. He died on December 8, 1995 in Rancho Santa Fe, California, USA.
